# @hostname=http://localhost:7071
@hostname=http://localhost:45233

### Submit feedback - positive

POST {{hostname}}/api/feedback HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "storeId": "store-001",
    "orderId": "ord-100",
    "customer": {
        "preferredName": "Milo Mustang",
        "firstName": "Milo",
        "lastName": "Mustang",
        "email": "milo.mustang@example.com",
        "phoneNumber": "555-0100",
        "preferredContactMethod": "Email"
    },
    "channel": "web",
    "rating": 4,
    "comment": "Great froyo! The staff was friendly and the flavors were delicious. Will definitely come back!"
}

